data.text:
For Blood or Money

Raylan hunts down Rachel's brother-in-law after he makes a violent escape from a halfway house.

Mindy Lahiri Is a Racist

When Danny invites one of his patients to write about the practice on her blog only to discover she is a white supremacist, the team hires a PR expert to help fix things.

That's No Ladyhat's My Cousin

Will and Carlton's (Will Smith, Alfonso Ribeiro) prep school goes coed; Aunt Vivian and Uncle Phil (Janet Hubert-Whitten, James Avery) make a startling announcement.

Baptism

Tommy copes with the loss of his father and a new man (Michael J. Fox) in Janet's life; Sheila finds a different way to deal with her issues; Sean, Franco and Mike concoct a surefire way to get rich.
